reviewText:
Is not a game i recommended for full price, but on sale, hell yeah.
the following game content are:
5 stage;
6 boss;
5 Difficulty;
Infinite combo battle system (like DMC);
Pantsu shot if you mash F12;
Ridiculs costume you never unlock untill you are a pervert.

the major problem is the sound, when you hit a enemy is terrible and music are too muchrepetitive.
I suggest this game for people having fun to complete DMC all difficulty or love pure action game.
